modName: The Erotic Adventures of Misty Skye CC - DELETED
descriptionHtml:
The Erotic Adventures of Misty Skye CC

I am not good at English, this is a machine translation.

We will replace our sisters and make it standalone, we will make equipment 7B.

Please overwrite after original introduction. Backup required.

Original credit

   All mod assets are either made by me or used by permission. 
   This mod is Nexus exclusive; this is a condition for free use of many custom assets.
   This mod would not be as sexy if not for the following:

Faces: Built with RaceMenu by Expired. 
"Misty Skye" and "Summer Skye" Presets available in optional download.
Hair: A couple of hott styles from KS Hairdos - Renewal by Kalilies Stealthic Khaos and Shocky.
Bodies: Modified from UNP by dimon99 using Bodyslide by Ousnius and Caliente. 
"Misty Skye" UUNP Preset available in optional download.
Outfits: New meshes were created with the invaluable help of Outfit Studio and Nifskope using little bits of various available resources 
(including Remodeled Armor for CBBE Bodyslide HDT by ChronoTrigger77, Remodeled Armor CBBEv3M by MAK 
and Steel Nord Plate Bikini Armor v2 by someone and kofman77, and a lot of altered vanilla game assets...)
Sword: A modified version of Discerner by Fowburner.
Skin textures: A modified mashup of Fair Skin Complexion by HHaleyy and Leyenda Skin by HeroedeLeyenda.
Skeleton: A modified XPMSE by Groovtama available in optional download.
HDT: Settings based on HDT Bounce and Jiggles UNP by Knightmare077 available in optional download.
Animation: Dance animations by Leito86 included, as seen in Sensual Cicero by Shubal. The characters in this mod do a lot of sexy 
dancing, and it works better if you've got sexy dance animations. Any loose files you are using to replace the vanilla dance animations 
will overwrite these. Install Sensual Cicero and run FNIS if the animations aren't working, or if you want to be extra sure, or just to 
endorse that mod cause it's good. 

2.0 Credits:

New outfits included in 2.0+ use (heavily altered) assets from:
Monno's Bikini by Monno
UNP Minidresses Collection by Tiwa44
Several awesome clothing resources originally created by Darigaz17 for Oblivion
Plus one outfit ported from The Witcher 2, courtesy of CD Projekt Red
All of which were used with explicit permission from the creators!

3.0 Credits:

Summer's unique dagger uses modified assets from Unique Uniques by InsanitySorrow.
  Mega thanks to all of the above.
  I think that's all, but this is a complicated mod. If I forgot anyone, please contact me.
  And finally: Sincere apologies to Skyrim's talented voice actors, whose voices have been 
  twisted and generally misused in the making of this mod.
